cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SY

This paper proposes a decision forest method for estimating information-theoretic quantities, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG), information theory (cs.IT), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The method is also applied to estimate the amount of information between neuron class and other cellular features, which falls under the category of neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) and systems and control (cs.SY).
